title: EMC Isilon Cluster information
agents: isilon
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors EMC Isilon Cluster status. Status will be {OK} if Isilon status is
 "OK" and {WARN} in any other case. Performance data is provide for  used, available
 and total disk size. 

 A perfometer is provided, that shows used capacity.


inventory:
 One service per Isilon cluster is created.

item:
 Isilon cluster <cluster name>
